{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"25f8eafd66","title":"康生谢富治接见云南省委书记赵健民时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ebbe8f5df","index":0,"year":1968,"month":1,"day":21,"articleId":"25f8eafd66","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"清理阶级队伍","id":"2e72dfc8f3","type":"主题"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"谢富治","id":"93cca4665d","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"},{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"521632adde","type":"title","text":"康生谢富治接见云南省委书记赵健民时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"39242fcd7c","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：1月21日凌晨，地点：京西宾馆二楼会议室。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d24ae59c37","type":"paragraph","text":"康生在谢富治陪同下步入会场。康生坐定后：“赵健民！”","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9e22e76d8","type":"paragraph","text":"“有。”赵健民站起身来，点了点头。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3492a816bb","type":"paragraph","text":"“你支持炮派，出了许多坏点子是不是？！”","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee4fa346a1","type":"paragraph","text":"赵健民摇头。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bae1b24387","type":"paragraph","text":"“赵健民，你为什么不回答？”谢富治，“你要回答康老提出的问题嘛！”","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f586e1b16","type":"paragraph","text":"“我没有支持炮派的错误行动。”赵健民答道，“现在云南形势很乱，我正要向中央汇报呢！到处停课、停产，武斗成风，这样下去……”","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7fafdd0cf2","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：“你放毒！刘少奇才骗我们，叛徒、特务才骗我们。我问你，你在白区工作是哪一年被捕的。”","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c862102d03","type":"paragraph","text":"赵健民：“我是1936年9 月被捕的。”","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c68a6d3d4","type":"paragraph","text":"“你在国民党监狱里是怎么自首的？！”","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab7e05ff56","type":"paragraph","text":"“我根本没有自首过。”","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4063eb1d65","type":"paragraph","text":"“你还在欺骗我们，你是叛徒。”","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4104ab1668","type":"paragraph","text":"“我就是被叛徒出卖才被捕的。康老，请问，说我是叛徒有什么根据？”","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9677381854","type":"paragraph","text":"“我再说一遍，你就是叛徒。凭我革命40年的经验，我有这个敏感，一眼就看出你是叛徒。”康生表情更冷酷。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87ffed0093","type":"paragraph","text":"“康老，你可要实事求是啊！凭敏感？哪有这个标准？！”","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bace9498ab","type":"paragraph","text":"康生站起来：“你疯狂得狠，你这个叛徒混进我们党里来，想乘文化大革命之机把边疆搞乱。我看到了国民党云南特务组织搞的一个计划，你们的行动，就是执行他们的计划。你要知道，我审过干，搞过情报，同特务作过斗争，我一眼就看出，你不是善类，你对我们有着刻骨的仇恨！”","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4acc3e2307","type":"paragraph","text":"赵健民：“说我是混进党内的叛徒，还有什么搞乱边疆的行动计划，这决不是事实。搞乱边疆的确大有人在，但不是我。我相信，假的真不了，真的假不了，谁是好人，谁是坏人，将来历史会证明的。我保留意见，请求中央审查。”","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8b20a5b126","type":"paragraph","text":"康生拍桌子：“不用你请求，一定要审查。我接触过那么多叛徒、特务、走资派，像你这样疯狂的还是不多的，你这是向无产阶级司令部进攻！你心里明白，什么样的下场在等着你。那好，你就保留吧，但要立刻写出要求审查的字据来。”","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8d0ca3aca","type":"paragraph","text":"赵健民他接过递过来的纸笔，写：","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef86438c53","type":"paragraph","text":"我在被捕期间，用生命保卫了党的利益，","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3bc5d8bc90","type":"paragraph","text":"特向党保证自己没有问题，请中央审查。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"240614a374","type":"paragraph","text":"赵健民   1968年1月21日夜","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c9343d84f","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：“现在决定，对赵健民实行监护审查。”","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"037bbb3c94","type":"paragraph","text":"（接着谢富治向他身后站着的人摆手，两个武装人员走上前，把赵健民反剪双手，拖下楼，送到秦城监狱。）","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"25f8eafd66","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}